{"h77c7fcc2g9a0ag4bfega9f6g0a556a79bfc0": ["Sweet child, you bore the pain like a true believer. ", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_RewardPenance.html", "e84e73da-b931-3d59-73dc-c142a8f2aeac"], "h2c467c06g1017g4c57gb476g4349f9756b0f": ["I could feel Loviatar's pleasure with every sting of my scourge.", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_RewardPenance.html", "264f231b-6ea5-d4d4-765f-264b448d03ba"], "ha7672307g80dfg4107ga3b8g723b23dd9321": ["I am proud to have served you this penance. ", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_RewardPenance.html", "304bd072-3fd6-bb43-b722-43d890c01ade"], "h1697b3b8g4067g4a95gb258g7d6e13d53b29": ["Thank you. I enjoyed myself.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_RewardPenance.html", "04390cda-1c6d-fd96-d424-2ab452ba38de"], "h65749661ge198g4089ga1feg6b04fa52ddec": ["As did I, dear one. ", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_RewardPenance.html", "3b8401bb-73d9-9bbf-ba1d-a7021a1dc1ff"], "he681969dge587g4575g9ca4gd250178c2759": ["Loviatar herself found your performance... inspiring. She has deemed you worthy of her blessing. ", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_RewardPenance.html", "6fbd4947-664f-560c-0b92-5f51e31b21bb"], "hc5bc4d07gafc9g454cgaaf7gf14851b58eba": ["And on a personal note, thank you. That was positively <i>divine. </i>", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_RewardPenance.html", "cfe89faf-3353-4903-b2ff-30644b2fd50c"], "hcc797c5fg3b73g4e6cg9853g6512f15b8125": ["It was an... interesting experience.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_RewardPenance.html", "bb33b58c-be40-bc5b-ac41-5086d78c739d"], "h5492093dgf01dg4698g966bg9818dca06f53": ["Interesting is an understatement, dear one. ", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_RewardPenance.html", "75e8d6a0-e994-8a45-63ce-97296e057a68"], "h4ccfd247ga95dg4c39ga758g96bb28dbdc52": ["I asked you for mercy!", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_RewardPenance.html", "ff20f8e5-712a-0bce-813c-ff872f4d9c0d"], "h3285aae3gf478g44c8g8a94g6c98816d50c7": ["I know, dear one. That was my favourite part. ", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_RewardPenance.html", "e748c2cc-d020-22f3-0c28-dd789977a6f2"], "hd45c5dcbga759g4d68gbf90ge10764c349c2": ["You could have hit me much harder.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_RewardPenance.html", "8d7a99e1-ce2f-bc73-60b0-4a2d9659ff3e"], "hd4b51f07g7e21g474ag8efag3b5bbaaad3a5": ["You're starting to sound like the Goddess herself, dear one. ", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_RewardPenance.html", "67fdb5f8-560c-d67e-596e-f20f667c1dc5"], "hc042718bg0f1fg4eadgaadfgdbe905e0c5fe": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_RewardPenance.html", "5dc7167b-4d23-0df4-b38b-0f1d853636a3"], "hdbf5924bgf901g4d70gb28fg305190e7b53f": ["Wait, penitent one. ", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_RewardPenance.html", "127a1743-5e46-edf5-08b2-f6f30f641772"], "hb904cfa9gf891g4af9g935bg231d675d6166": ["I could feel Loviatar's pleasure with every slice of my dagger.", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_RewardPenance.html", "d9420d36-9717-7dc6-7af0-fd148dcd162b"], "h2b48609egb19fg4fe8g89a6g742007e9b953": ["I could feel Loviatar's pleasure with every swing of my axe.", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_RewardPenance.html", "1c693b5a-fc5c-2457-5441-14dbae6d5eeb"], "h7cc33595g1bd6g47e4g962dg200c5127e279": ["Sweet child. While I enjoyed that, I'm afraid your reaction was... lacking.", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_RewardPenance.html", "25b7c8bb-cc94-d9f7-f88f-1132d28e3521"], "hdd9201c0g880fg4705ga53dgd3fb52ef75ac": ["To gain Loviatar's favour, ever <i>single </i>strike should be met with an honest cry of pain - or perhaps a touch of begging.", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_RewardPenance.html", "3e1031f0-5dc5-ae8c-158f-22c9fbab3375"], "h294b3d60gcb2cg43e8ga5d0gba9b1d1fcc37": ["Nevertheless, thank you. And I pray you've learned from today's little... lesson.", "cad1854b-8f41-4038-b640-156ee0272f81", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_PainPriest_RewardPenance.html", "d51c4eb9-9a12-63aa-04bc-d25e2176185d"]}